{"tid":1688561,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"其實香港人到呢加知唔知一輸會變成點？","createTime":"2019-11-02T13:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T14:20:15.000Z","uid":5737,"like":28,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7f152116f0895d5664720d468be0686af29a6a3e","tid":1688561,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iTNnXJh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiTNnXJh.png&h=fa1abcb3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nJAXMBH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnJAXMBH.png&h=e05428d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k3hrEWK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk3hrEWK.png&h=c33246c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QxzQ6DZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQxzQ6DZ.png&h=27e81dcf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A81zOP7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA81zOP7.png&h=a805a320&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UWJB2a1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUWJB2a1.png&h=c57b43a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n到時我地一輸就會入收容區<br />\n每次出去都要許可證<br />\n就憑佢呢加連跑步 都要申請就知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5個月啦 香港人仲要屈服白色恐怖當中<br />\n明明我人都多過佢<br />\n點解唔反抗<br />\n香港人！ 反抗 ！<br />\n呢個口號 個反抗 去左邊？<br />\n希望你地知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一輸就會變成以上既圖咁<br />\n就算比人殺左都要多謝佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa063b3f5d81abe041696b795c8d01a7fc34fd7","tid":1688561,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,